attr.title: Astronautilus
attr.desc: Your ship has crash-landed on a stray rogue planet, and you're out of fuel ... It's up to you to delve beneath the frozen surface and find a way to get your ship back into space. Fight strange sea creatures and uncover the mysteries of the world beneath the ice!
attr.inst: Purchase the game from itch.io (https://neozoid-games.itch.io/astronautilus). Download, extract, and copy the game files to the astronautilus/assets directory. Alternatively, you can use the free demo version files.
attr.inst_md: Purchase the game from [itch.io](https://neozoid-games.itch.io/astronautilus). Download, extract, and copy the game files to the `astronautilus/assets` directory. Alternatively, you can use the free demo version files.
